 - 300 g double cream","½ tsp salt","½ tsp ground cumin","½ tsp sweet paprika","2 Tbsp fresh coriander, leaves only, chopped"]}],"id":"r150814","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-MAckgZKn3mI\/XZaq1DCVpJI\/AAAAAAAAhhc\/dlTG4yc90JofHfJLAbU4Lwib4p-HT3MsACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_poyTl--aQGyWTjN6.png","title":"Chicken Corn Chowder, Broccoli Terrines","publishedAt":"2017-06-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19 g","fat":"27 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"10 g","calories":"1537 kJ \/ 367 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ceramic ramekins (Ø max. 7 cm x height 4.5 cm)","hintsAndTricks":["<i>Thermomix helps you prepare a meal for eight people with less than <b>40 minutes<b> spent in the kitchen! Serve the creamy chicken corn chowder as a starter followed by the broccoli terrines as a light main course.<\/i>","To keep broccoli terrines warm while you enjoy the chowder, set covered Varoma with broccoli terrines on the empty but still warm mixing bowl.<br>- Turn out terrines onto a plate for an attractive presentation.<br>- Broccoli terrines can also be served as a starter or as a side dish, for example, with smoked salmon or roasted meat.<br>- Instead of ramekins, use heatproof glass jars or metal moulds. If using metal moulds, reduce cooking time by <b>2 minutes<b> in <b>step 7.<b>"],"basicInfo":["easy","35m","1h 25m","8 portions"]}